  "text": "The ensemble with stochastic dynamics seems to capture some signal for the extreme winter 2009/10 635 [CITATION_1] , as shown in supplementary fig. S7 . For the other three regimes, no significant change is found. This encouraging result should be interpreted with caution due to the high levels of uncertainty when dealing with seasonal re-forecasts over mid-latitudes (Shi et al., 2015) .",
